data.meta_description: ICC2013 Proceedings - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. 26 International Cartographic Conference August 25 - 30, 2013 Dresden, Germany proceedings this work is a compilation of contributions to the ICC Conference 2013 at Dresden. The setting: Dresden boasts a significant quantity of world-class art treasures and can in this respect cope with places like Venice or Florence but also with cities like athens, London, Paris, Moscow, Berlin, or Rome.
